			<h2><a href="/blog/techmonitor-cloud-migration/">Planning a cloud migration? Here are 27 things to consider</a></h2>
			<h3>Published <time>5 October 2020</time> in <a href="https://mariothomas.com/categories/aws/">AWS</a>  | 10 minute read | <a href="/blog/techmonitor-cloud-migration/"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Permalink" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		
		<p>From peak CPU and peak RAM, to decommissioning costs, there&rsquo;s more to think about than TCO. How can you assess (at a detailed level) whether migrating X application to the cloud is going to make sense for your organisation?</p>
		
